like ganas were dedicated

35
00:12:53,917 --> 00:12:56,166
to Shiva alone.

36
00:12:56,959 --> 00:13:02,709
So, She wanted to have Her own Son

37
00:13:03,875 --> 00:13:05,959
who can

38
00:13:11,291 --> 00:13:13,875
permeate

39
00:13:16,583 --> 00:13:21,333
Her powers on this Earth.

40
00:13:30,375 --> 00:13:37,083
So to begin with when the Shakti created this Universe

41
00:13:37,583 --> 00:13:41,667
and Sadashiva was watching Her creation,

42
00:13:41,999 --> 00:13:48,333
the first thing She created on this Earth was innocence

43
00:13:48,959 --> 00:13:54,999
and the embodiment of that innocence was Shri Ganesha.

44
00:13:57,458 --> 00:14:02,750
The whole Universe was covered with innocence,

45
00:14:03,166 --> 00:14:08,959
which we call as Omkara.

46
00:14:13,917 --> 00:14:22,999
This innocence protected all the creation of the world

47
00:14:23,458 --> 00:14:27,291
and penetrated into all that is matter.

48
00:14:27,625 --> 00:14:31,458
Matter is innocent.

49
00:14:34,792 --> 00:14:37,625
If you hit the matter, it will hit you back

50
00:14:38,041 --> 00:14:40,000
because it is built like that.

51
00:14:40,417 --> 00:14:44,333
It doesn’t want to harm you by any method

52
00:14:44,709 --> 00:14:46,917
except that if you try to hit it,

53
00:14:47,250 --> 00:14:53,667
it hits you back, in its own nature.

54
00:14:55,583 --> 00:14:58,250
So it was called as Jada,

55
00:14:58,583 --> 00:15:06,458
the one that acts according to the built-in nature.

56
00:15:09,792 --> 00:15:15,417
Innocence in the animals is of another kind,

57
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,917
where the animals do not know

58
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:21,250
that they are committing crimes.

59
00:15:21,667 --> 00:15:23,583
Animals

60
00:15:25,709 --> 00:15:30,000
when they say, kill an animal, another animal,

61
00:15:33,834 --> 00:15:36,458
or trespass your properties,

62
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,041
create nuisance all over,

63
