634
01:10:36,667 --> 01:10:39,834
Do they make a noise?

635
01:10:40,208 --> 01:10:40,959
No?

636
01:10:41,999 --> 01:10:43,500
So we can get you better ones.

637
01:10:43,792 --> 01:10:45,417
Let Me see how big your feet are.

638
01:10:45,834 --> 01:10:48,917
Let Me see. They’re very small, aren’t they.

639
01:10:49,291 --> 01:10:51,709
You are a big girl or a small girl?

640
01:10:52,125 --> 01:10:56,291
Small? No, no, she’s big, she can stand up, let's see?

641
01:10:56,709 --> 01:11:03,959
Let’s see. Hallo. Come along, come here.

642
01:11:12,000 --> 01:11:14,999
What’s the matter with her?

643
01:11:15,542 --> 01:11:19,917
She always like this?

644
01:11:20,709 --> 01:11:22,875
We’ll call her Siddhi. This is the power.

645
01:11:23,250 --> 01:11:25,250
Siddhi is a good name.

646
01:11:38,208 --> 01:11:41,875
All right. May God bless you.

647
01:11:41,999 --> 01:11:43,792
She’ll be all right.

648
01:12:09,041 --> 01:12:13,458
Look at that. Take a picture.

649
01:12:13,709 --> 01:12:18,000
May God bless you. May God bless you.

650
01:12:18,375 --> 01:12:21,583
Get up now. All right.

651
01:12:21,999 --> 01:12:25,375
You must get up. Come here. Come here. Aah.

652
01:12:25,750 --> 01:12:27,417
So now we’ll call him as Vinayaka.

653
01:12:27,750 --> 01:12:32,875
That’s the name of Shri Ganesha, Vinayaka.

654
01:12:42,083 --> 01:12:44,333
Who else is there?

655
01:12:49,333 --> 01:12:50,667
Come along.

656
01:13:14,417 --> 01:13:19,542
Hello. We’ll call him Ganapati.

657
01:13:51,625 --> 01:13:54,125
May God bless you.

658
01:13:54,999 --> 01:14:01,792
Come here. We’ll call them as Gauri and Ganesha.

659
01:14:06,083 --> 01:14:10,041
Gauri and Ganesha.

660
01:14:10,792 --> 01:14:12,333
Can you come?

661
01:14:33,792 --> 01:14:39,500
Ganesha’s another name is Omkara. We’ll call him Omkara.

662
01:14:41,625 --> 01:14:44,875
May God bless you.

663
01:14:46,750 --> 01:14:50,709
Come here. Good. You are Omkara now. All right?

664
01:14:51,041 --> 01:14:55,375
Good name, Omkara.

665
01:15:30,417 --> 01:15:32,542
So now...

666
01:15:35,959 --> 01:15:43,083
Ramma. Ramma is name of the Devi, name of Parvati.

667
01:15:51,041 --> 01:15:55,125
Is the name of the Mother of Ganesha, Ramma.

668
01:15:55,583 --> 01:16:05,417
Ramma is the one that plays in the heart.

669
01:16:11,625 --> 01:16:13,417
Janaki. Janaki.

670
01:17:18,291 --> 01:17:21,083
Sharmila, Sharmadayini, Sharmila, Sharmadayani

671
01:17:26,917 --> 01:17:28,417
Sharmadayani is the bliss-giver.

672
01:17:28,667 --> 01:17:32,709
Giver of bliss. Giver of bliss.

673
01:17:44,458 --> 01:17:46,125
Sharmila is the name of the Goddess.

674
01:17:46,625 --> 01:17:49,583
She’s the giver of bliss, Sharmadayani,

